This is a project inpired by moviebarcode(http://moviebarcode.tumblr.com/)

It provides a simple shell script which compress a whole movie to a moviebarcode picture.

It prefer Linux as a test platform since the necessary tools such as bash, graphicsmagick, bc, ffmpeg is running better on Linux rather than on Windows. 

This simple project is distributed under the GPL v3 License, you can contact the author<xiaohanyu1988@gmail.com> for details.
